OL,3,CKnife crime up by more than a fifth
OL,4,Cacross the Capital
OL,6,FThe official statistics come as the
OL,7,FGovernment has defended the fact a
OL,8,Flong-promised ban on zombie knives
OL,9,Fwill not come into force until the
OL,10,Fautumn, a year after it was promised
OL,11,Fby Rishi Sunak.
OL,13,FFresh legislation is to be laid in
OL,14,FParliament to tackle zombie-style
OL,15,Fweapons, with the ban due to come into
OL,16,Fforce in September making it illegal
OL,17,Fto possess, sell, manufacture or
OL,18,Ftransport the blades.
